{"type": "article", "id": 3128, "title": "可以喷雾的淋浴喷头", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-29T07:25:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232718iyNwK7Gdu92hk1Wp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t冬天快要到了，走进没有浴霸与暖气的浴室需要勇气。怎样才能在洗浴过程中保持温暖呢？浙江大学的学生们为我们想出了一个妙招，那就是 Vapo 。一般人洗澡时，在涂抹浴液的情况下，出于节约水的考虑，都会将淋浴喷头关闭，但在浙江大学学生的这一设计方案中，淋浴喷头将会持续运行，只不过它会转为喷雾的状态，以保持周身的温暖与湿润，又能够达到节约水资源的目的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232715VMvEIcuTR4N6oxH5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232716s8C9MilYupUw6kyR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232716cUg0PTkiuJ2htM7v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.60625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232717TFCM3LgsnEmDjKx8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.896875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}